---
title: Tex-Mex Chicken & Basmati Rice with Cucumber Salad & Garlic Aioli
description: A tasty Tex-Mex style bowl that the whole family will love. Fragrant rice adds a tonne of flavour to the base of this dish and you’ll love this marinade for the diced chicken. Quick and easy, who could resist!?
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tex-mex-chicken-rice-bowl-7a0b3adb.jpg
